meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) > 0 THEN 'with PR' ELSE 'without PR' END AS "PR Indicator"

axis0.name: PR Indicator
axis0.text:
CASE 
  WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' )> 0
  THEN 'with PR' 
  ELSE 'without PR' 
END

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" ) = 1 THEN NULL WHEN "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" IN ( 'B' ) THEN 'automated' ELSE 'manual' END AS "Automation" FORMAT "%"

axis0.name: Automation
axis0.text:
CASE
     WHEN ISNULL( "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 1
         THEN NULL
     WHEN  "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" IN (<%= auto_user_type %>)
         THEN 'automated'
     ELSE 'manual'
END

axis2.name: #{Automation}
axis2.text:
100*AVG(CASE
    WHEN ("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" = <%= auto_user_type %>)
    THEN 1.0
    WHEN ("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" != <%= auto_user_type %>)
    THEN 0.0
    WHEN ISNULL("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE") = 1
    THEN 0.0
    ELSE 0.0
END
)

axis2.name: #{NonCataloguePORatio}
axis2.text:
AVG(CASE 
  WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."MATNR") = 1
  THEN 1.0
  ELSE 0.0
END)*100

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( "EKPO"."MATNR" ) = 1 THEN 'Non-Catalogue Order' ELSE 'Catalogue Order' END AS "Cataloge or Non-Catalogue Order"

axis0.name: Cataloge or Non-Catalogue Order
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."MATNR") = 1 
    THEN 
        'Non-Catalogue Order'
    ELSE 
        'Catalogue Order'
END
